  "texts": [
    "In symptomatic MM, patients with more than 7 MRI sites had a poor prognosis, while patients with less than or equal to 7 sites had a similar survival rate.",
    "(Routine MRI sequences, in addition to showing MM infiltration pattern and number of sites, can also semiquantify the degree of bone marrow infiltration.)",
    "MethodologyIn this study, the consistency between Morphogo and cell morphology in plasma cell recognition was also good.",
    "In AI-MRD VS.M-MRD, the Kappa value of Kappa induction test continued to increase with the increase of the number of recognized cells, and Kappa=0.667(P=0.001) in the 2000 group, indicating that the results of AI-MRD and M-MRD were highly consistent when the recognition level of AI cells reached 2000.",
    "In further data analysis, the sensitivity and accuracy of MRD results between AI and cell morphology also increased significantly with the increase of the number of cells recognized by AI, and the specificity was always maintained at the level of 90% to 100%."
